{"tid":832831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度捷特機師忘記為機艙加壓　30多名乘客耳鼻流血","createTime":"2018-09-23T05:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T10:06:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9fbd30fdcac0ab4af35305ac1ebe1e187937afa5","tid":832831,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1419359-20180921.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1419359-20180921.htm&d=2LZLcimHF0yWJPl20c45AS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=79421405\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1419359-20180921.htm&h=10abc5d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1419359-20180921.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n印度捷特航空一架客機在爬升時，機師忘記開啟機艙加壓裝置，導致30多名乘客耳鼻流血。航空公司為事件致歉，涉事的機師停職接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n涉事客機載著166名乘客和5名機組人員，星期四原定由孟買飛去拉賈斯坦邦首府齋浦爾，客機在起飛後大約45分鐘，導致機艙內氣壓下跌，飛機其後折返孟買，安全降落。"},{"pid":"5b3e6ac3a0fb9c7f4a55ecc85441eabd2d5abcdc","tid":832831,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"加壓唔係自動嘅咩"},{"pid":"94e80e089ba81db873b858fe1b240cec699a2d12","tid":832831,"uid":132587,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://farm3.staticflickr.com/2155/2333363652_784bbc31a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm3.staticflickr.com%2F2155%2F2333363652_784bbc31a8.jpg&h=386cbfd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2cfc4752f8fc3be036d99769699b34478ca167c","tid":832831,"uid":20414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b3e6ac3a0fb9c7f4a55ecc85441eabd2d5abcdc","tid":832831,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"加壓唔係自動嘅咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"會有警號架喎<br />\n你估似太陽神客機咩"},{"pid":"504f52084a730098ce9c1a01cefa7b